title: Best Bits with Abby: PART 1

description:
Abby joins Morgan this week and they talk about the things they’ve tried recently that were really gross, some recent moments they’ve felt old, and strange childhood habits they had. Abby shared her highlights and lowlights this year. Morgan talked about a really bad day she had, and the crazy country concert she saw recently.
